"tid":252981,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T04:51:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的，我喺30歲嘅關口前回眸一望，發現大學畢業以黎自己做黎做去嘅都係人工低工時長嘅西工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 莫講話幸福快樂，連可以獨立自主嘅生活都看似與我無緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打絲打都有/經歷過呢啲困窘？我想轉行但唔知可以做乜，考政府工又一直石沈大海，想搵人幫但求助無門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家日日返工都好似受僱去做M奴咁，每日起身就係想唔撈，但唔撈又唔知下一份可以做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求各路巴絲指點我迷津，我唔想就咁一世丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n或者我有限度自爆多少少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我non 3大社科畢業，當時係個摺到冇得再摺嘅毒拎（依家好左）。出黎做左兩年文員仔，深感咁樣唔得就去讀左個19 master，然後入左行做物管2年，上年年尾轉左行去做電腦排版到到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知自己冇乜實力去同人爭工做，但我都想上流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家勤操gym去搏考紀律部隊，亦都多左睇時事新聞禁玩facebook，而除此之外就唔知可以做啲乜去增值自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係個people person，而依家份工嘅性質堅唔適合自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 恨錯難返，除左去ifc跳落去重練之外我重可以點俾多次機會自己？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b1b566d29aad21b5ed4178bb7411dadafde0e3","tid":252981,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:48:27.000Z","msg":"認真post冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706570a1d7a197868078990007cca357b78836ad","tid":252981,